description: Overview of ElastiCache CloudWatch metrics. Provides both host-level metrics (for example, CPU usage) and redis engine metrics
title: AWS ElastiCache Redis

50910278-a96b-4bae-a3b4-4c5b9e7cdefc.name: cache_cluster_id
50910278-a96b-4bae-a3b4-4c5b9e7cdefc.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'cache_cluster_id') as cache_cluster_id
FROM signoz_metrics.distributed_time_series_v4_1day
WHERE metric_name like 'aws_elasticache_%'
GROUP BY cache_cluster_id
